data.description: Welcome to this stunning newer construction home, built in 2019. Located in the Willow Heights Neighborhood. This 4 bedroom, 2 bath residence features an inviting open floor concept, ideal for both entertaining and everyday living. As you step inside, you'll be immediately greeted by the airy and bright atmosphere created by the open layout. The main living area seamlessly connects the living room, dining space, and kitchen, providing a harmonious flow for gatherings. The home has wood plank tile floors throughout the main living area, granite counter tops, maple cabinets, stainless gas range and appliances, and tankless water heater. The primary suite is a generously sized bedroom with a walk-in closet and a beautiful en-suite bathroom. A Smart home system with Smartcode deadbolt and LED upgraded lighting package. Outside, you'll find a well-maintained yard and covered patio with a pergola making it perfect for outdoor entertaining.
